Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起你最想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後宮王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算是收到一個笨蛋小弟了嗎
